To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MatHold _mathold;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_mathold = MatHold(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_mathold.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "period", _mathold.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "mathold", _mathold.Current);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.mathold = self.MatHold(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.mathold.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "period", self.mathold.Period)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "mathold", self.mathold.Current)

For more information about plotting indicators, see Plotting Indicators.
